  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off endless waves of zombies and monsters in Horde Together, a co-op survival game built for action and chaos. Team up, scavenge for gear, and see how long you can survive the apocalypse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore ever-changing levels packed with loot, hazards, and undead surprises. We’ll be rolling out fresh maps and content constantly during Early Access to keep things exciting.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Assemble Your Team</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.poster.avif?t=1747839324\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.webm?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.mp4?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No one survives alone! Team up with up to 4 friends and assemble your perfect monster-slaying crew.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your friends get overwhelmed—and then try not to follow</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laugh, panic, and scream together with built-in proximity voice chat (coming soon)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle the Horde</strong></h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.poster.avif?t=1747839324\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.webm?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.mp4?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create private lobbies for just your friends, or jump into a public game and team up with strangers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revive fallen teammates mid-wave… if you’re brave enough to try</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival is brutal, fast-paced, and endlessly replayable</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Ultimate Armory</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/012ea16f41c6688942915d563e468455.poster.avif?t=1747839324\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/012ea16f41c6688942915d563e468455.webm?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/012ea16f41c6688942915d563e468455.mp4?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge for weapons, ammo, and upgrades scattered across each map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find rare items and secrets hidden throughout each level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your arsenal between rounds to keep up with tougher threats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New maps, enemies, and gear are added regularly throughout Early Access</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off endless waves of zombies and monsters in Horde Together, a co-op survival game built for action and chaos. Team up, scavenge for gear, and see how long you can survive the apocalypse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore ever-changing levels packed with loot, hazards, and undead surprises. We’ll be rolling out fresh maps and content constantly during Early Access to keep things exciting.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Assemble Your Team</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.poster.avif?t=1747839324\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.webm?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/043d008b23c43185ad1c19814e68be83.mp4?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No one survives alone! Team up with up to 4 friends and assemble your perfect monster-slaying crew.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your friends get overwhelmed—and then try not to follow</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laugh, panic, and scream together with built-in proximity voice chat (coming soon)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle the Horde</strong></h2></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.poster.avif?t=1747839324\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.webm?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/dab1188724ab5d6a20f9c098893a8762.mp4?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create private lobbies for just your friends, or jump into a public game and team up with strangers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revive fallen teammates mid-wave… if you’re brave enough to try</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival is brutal, fast-paced, and endlessly replayable</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Ultimate Armory</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/012ea16f41c6688942915d563e468455.poster.avif?t=1747839324\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/012ea16f41c6688942915d563e468455.webm?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212140/extras/012ea16f41c6688942915d563e468455.mp4?t=1747839324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge for weapons, ammo, and upgrades scattered across each map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find rare items and secrets hidden throughout each level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your arsenal between rounds to keep up with tougher threats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New maps, enemies, and gear are added regularly throughout Early Access</p></li></ul>",
